### Guidelines for agents
- Use `playwright-cli snapshot` to get element references before `click` or `fill`
- Always guard with `command -v playwright-cli &>/dev/null` — skip silently if unavailable
- Prefer `agent test` wrappers for CMUX-integrated testing
- Use named sessions (`-s=name`) when running multiple browsers in parallel

